{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/chips-heroes-uprising-tower-game/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Mentahkan Serangan Alien di Game CHIPS: Heroes Uprising!","content":"<p>Setelah sukses dengan game perdananya, <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ciayo-games-merilis-chips-monster-tap/\">CHIPS: Monster Tap</a>, CIAYO Games kini kembali hadir dengan game terbaru mereka, CHIPS: Heroes Uprising. Di game terbaru produksi divisi game CIAYO Corp. ini, petualangan Chips, Crocket dan Coco kini tampil dengan <em>gameplay</em> yang segar dan lebih menantang!</p>\n<p>Masih bersetting di Chammyland, pulau yang tentram ini kini kedatangan tamu yang tak hanya tidak diundang, tapi juga tidak menyenangkan. Sepasukan alien turun dan mengisolir seluruh pulau Chammyland. Para penduduk Chammyland ditangkapi, bahkan Crocket dan Coco.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_48885\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48885\" data-attachment-id=\"48885\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/chips-heroes-uprising-tower-game/attachment/01-chips-heroes-uprising/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-chips-heroes-uprising.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-chips-heroes-uprising\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-chips-heroes-uprising-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-chips-heroes-uprising.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48885\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-chips-heroes-uprising.jpg\" alt=\"chips: heroes uprising\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-chips-heroes-uprising.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-chips-heroes-uprising-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48885\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Games</p></div>\n<p>Hanya Chips yang selamat, dan ia berambisi untuk menyelamatkan teman-temannya serta penduduk Chammyland yang lain. Untuk itu, Chips menggunakan berbagai bangunan di kota sebagai markas pertahanan. Bisakah Chips menyelamatkan Chammyland dari serangan alien? Dan apa tujuan para alien tersebut menguasai Chammyland?</p>\n<p>Dalam game <em>action-RPG</em> ini, <em>gamer</em> ditugaskan untuk membangun berbagai macam <em>tower</em> untuk mementahkan serangan alien. Setiap <em>tower</em> bisa diperkuat dengan menambahkan karakter <em>hero</em> dan juga peralatan khusus. Semakin solid kekuatan <em>tower</em>, <em>hero</em> dan persenjataan mereka, semakin mudah pula menghalau serangan alien.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_48886\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48886\" data-attachment-id=\"48886\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/chips-heroes-uprising-tower-game/attachment/02-chips-heroes-uprising/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/02-chips-heroes-uprising.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-chips-heroes-uprising\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/02-chips-heroes-uprising-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/02-chips-heroes-uprising.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48886\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/02-chips-heroes-uprising.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Games\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/02-chips-heroes-uprising.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/02-chips-heroes-uprising-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48886\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Games</p></div>\n<p>Untuk menambah kemampuan <em>tower</em>, <em>hero</em>, dan senjata mereka, <em>gamer</em> bisa melakukan ekspedisi untuk mencari berbagai bahan dan material. Material ini kemudian akan dijadikan bahan <em>crafting</em> untuk membuat dan menambah kekuatan <em>tower</em>, <em>hero</em>, dan senjata.</p>\n<p>Jika pertahanan <em>tower</em> sudah sangat kuat, maka sudah saatnya untuk menyerang balik para alien! <em>Gamer</em> bisa menyerang markas alien untuk mendapatkan berbagai <em>loot</em> dan <em>item</em> berharga, bahkan <em>tower</em> baru. <em>Gamer</em> juga bisa menyerang <em>tower</em> milik <em>gamer</em> lainnya dalam Raid Mode, untuk mencari <em>loot</em> tambahan.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_48887\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48887\" data-attachment-id=\"48887\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/chips-heroes-uprising-tower-game/attachment/03-chips-heroes-uprising/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/03-chips-heroes-uprising.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-chips-heroes-uprising\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/03-chips-heroes-uprising-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/03-chips-heroes-uprising.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48887\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/03-chips-heroes-uprising.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Games\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/03-chips-heroes-uprising.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/03-chips-heroes-uprising-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48887\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Games</p></div>\n<p>CHIPS: Heroes Uprising akan rilis untuk <em>platform mobile</em> Android dan iOS. Walaupun saat ini game tersebut masih dikembangkan CIAYO Games, <em>gamer</em> bisa mencoba versi beta-nya hanya di Bekraf Game Prime 2018! Jangan sampai kehabisan tiketnya dengan registrasi di <a href=\"http://bit.ly/bgp2018\">bit.ly/bgp2018</a>.</p>\n<p>Untuk informasi lebih lanjut tentang CHIPS: Heroes Uprising dan CIAYO Games, kunjungi website CIAYO Games di <a href=\"http://games.ciayo.com/\">http://games.ciayo.com</a></p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"af5d232e-d494-5961-92d4-ece5e762acd1"}}}